Class MarginLeft

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.webfirmframework.wffweb.css.core.AbstractCssProperty<MarginLeft>
      • com.webfirmframework.wffweb.css.MarginLeft
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CssProperty, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class MarginLeft
extends AbstractCssProperty<MarginLeft>
     The margin-left property sets the left margin of an element.

 Note: Negative values are allowed.
 Default value:  0
 Inherited:      no
 Animatable:     yes
 Version:        CSS1
 JavaScript syntax:      object.style.marginLeft="100px"
    Since:
    1.0.0
